Gunmen on Wednesday shot dead one Adams Amakel,in Sapele, Sapele Local Government Area of Delta State. DAILY POST gathered that the deceased, popularly referred to as Ten over Ten, was killed after he opened a new hair dressing saloon in the area. Details as to why he was killed were still sketchy at the time of this report. It was, however, learnt that the gunmen stormed the area in a Toyota Corolla car that had no number plate and shot him twice on his chest. When contacted for comments, the Delta State Police Public Relations Officer, DSP Onome Onovwakpoyeya, confirmed the development. The PRO said, “Somebody was shot dead. 10/10. Yes, it’s true.”